{"tid":106182,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"課金俾品客參選既入一入黎","createTime":"2017-02-03T12:32:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-04T17:59:48.000Z","uid":10879,"like":58,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"318dfe4e954933bacefb1dcb6d9189a0e1d39ab6","tid":106182,"uid":10879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T12:32:39.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">平民損錢俾有錢佬參選咁撚好笑?<br />\n仲係民主派人覺得咁樣可以用民意向中共施壓令佢當選咁撚天真?<br />\n青政JR你班傻西唔撚損都算喇 你地泛民嗰四個都做唔到一日籌100 萬啦<br />\n你班on9走去課金俾建制有錢佬參選?<br />\n人唔笑 狗都吠<br />\n屌你老母雨革/魚革之後都無撚進步過</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03f013856590f7ace6adc14895556ddc591d9b70","tid":106182,"uid":9348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T12:41:02.000Z","msg":"駁唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"702e42cc458a6595e7580e30e392c429c21d8d88","tid":106182,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T12:42:37.000Z","msg":"太空傻閪"},{"pid":"c4a70f1d4104d300a8c08210abc89b7610f6be77","tid":106182,"uid":72037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T12:44:06.000Z","msg":"香港人根本就退步 衰過以前 共匪見到咁仲唔笑撚死"},{"pid":"998edb6656c9067bd593167c56815fe130042665","tid":106182,"uid":10879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T12:52:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港人根本就退步 衰過以前 共匪見到咁仲唔笑撚死</blockquote><br />\n課完金仲要係social network打status<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4bec86176e26176614e4d96852cea8ed9637858","tid":106182,"uid":33099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T12:53:13.000Z","msg":"獨立/建國你又得個講字<br />\n<br />\nD 人渴望最少有良治<br />\n<br />\n咁都有錯？<br />\n<br />\n咁你又有乜策略可以幫到香港？"},{"pid":"0ee8079c084124255fcb9057b50240ab96fff4b9","tid":106182,"uid":10879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T13:03:57.000Z","msg":"<bloc